[30;1m42 | [0m[35m    This pass works on a scheduled, physical circuit. It scans the circuit for[0m
[30;1m43 | [0m[35m    idle periods of time (i.e. those containing delay instructions) and inserts[0m
[30;1m44 | [0m[35m    a DD sequence of gates in those spots. These gates amount to the identity,[0m

[30;1m48 | [0m[35m    * Measurements and resets on disjoint qubits happen simultaneously and are part of the same bloc[0m
[30;1m49 | [0m[35m    """[0m
